教傳統制度得以保留，再加上中東國家多為政教合一體系，伊斯蘭教係統治者得以延續權威，維持社會秩序嘅一大根本，冇可能俾你啲蟻民話唔信就唔信<br />\n<br />\n雖然宜家都有唔少國家開始行世俗化(印尼、馬來西亞、土耳其等)，但要喺人權、自由方面要同西方睇齊都係有一段距離<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"31e13b9843506f9653ef2c246dfaa856438da5cb","tid":621012,"uid":125646,"like":8,"dislike":1,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-08T03:57:07.000Z","msg":"主要係黑力架同蝻先會信呢啲教，不了"},{"pid":"adc38676b1af9eddd943e20f24bbfecedfab1622","tid":621012,"uid":152123,"like":10,"dislike":1,"score":9,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-08T04:15:11.000Z","msg":"咁你政教分離 啟蒙咗未先？<br />\n成日拎自己同耶教比 人唔笑狗都吠啦<br />\n淨係識拎百幾二百年前嘅耶教同自己比<br />\n不如你拎埋舊約時代做比較啦<br />\n咁咪證明你個教冇進步過囉<br />\n多人信又點 你哋年中內戰死幾多信徒"},{"pid":"7fd84af81fd44da2ef8709d2c6c9352d487c55e2","tid":621012,"uid":152123,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"31e13b9843506f9653ef2c246dfaa856438da5cb","tid":621012,"uid":125646,"like":8,"dislike":1,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-08T03:57:07.000Z","msg":"主要係黑力架同蝻先會信呢啲教，不了"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-08T04:15:26.000Z","msg":"黑人都唔係信呢啲"},{"pid":"86227dfe698f25b1d3a18046da28264654cb544e","tid":621012,"uid":17232,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8263ca3b0d3996363abd0724bcaee97631658a04","tid":621012,"uid":89046,"like":1,"dislike":19,"score":-18,"quote":{"pid":"c0d8762648fdcc5758e0206ff6b6c4b51e13bcf6","tid":621012,"uid":17232,"like":8,"dislike":2,"score":6,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-04-08T03:03:35.000Z","msg":"不安<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-08T03:21:18.000Z","msg":"現時全球伊斯蘭教信徒數量接近二十億，並有望於不久將來取代耶教成為世界第一大宗教 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-08T04:46:58.000Z","msg":"世界好危險<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"db8a7f830f36903caa6495b583f5fa39e73595ba","tid":621012,"uid":170044,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a838685cdd7514e0f13184be65ce4bab69a14d01","tid":621012,"uid":92376,"l